                  "title": "Intent and target mode",
                  "summary": "Describe what kind of artifact this is and how Twilite should interpret it."
                },
                {
                  "key": "bindings",
                  "title": "Surface bindings",
                  "summary": "Choose the primary views and keep the declaration's surface contract aligned."
                },
                {
