      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Declaration\n\nA declaration names the graph, carries intent, identifies the default surface, and lists the named surfaces the graph exposes to readers and other graphs.\n\nThis class graph now models those surfaces as actual `port` specimens so the contract is visible on the canvas instead of being implied by generic view nodes.",
